bbcb51e2f029678d","tid":1525780,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85c732cf6df73300a68530579f8f4a7ed2e08dd4","tid":1525780,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n果陣又唔見班狗有「專業判斷」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"佢地既專業就係唔專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec056ac5e6a7d28f8850bdce911acb282a12235","tid":1525780,"uid":49546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a54edb86b9326906966370ab058d6e84352d86a","tid":1525780,"uid":45255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"著黑衫唔一定係暴徙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔係著黑衣都話你換左衫"},{"pid":"45f5f3212d6536c34f8fdfcca33bdd513e420c2c","tid":1525780,"uid":18210,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n完整示範片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=729f56e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"3a68463643aa91b86636287964c098dfd3af3d61","tid":1525780,"uid":188374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/28/163826_5f9a9c3765a2e0b0d871d42e17360b1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F28%2F163826_5f9a9c3765a2e0b0d871d42e17360b1a.jpg&h=72ed58e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ae6a6a0c3d6928aa3d9f148befeca19f6c9d719","tid":1525780,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ec056ac5e6a7d28f8850bdce911acb282a12235","tid":1525780,"uid":49546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a54edb86b9326906966370ab058d6e84352d86a","tid":1525780,"uid":45255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:58:12.000Z","msg":"著黑衫唔一定係暴徙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔係著黑衣都話你換左衫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"拉左直情除埋你衫"},{"pid":"f61c339b2746ff5c4e0318110ce5ff9b42d2cf3b","tid":1525780,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"好奇一問<br />\n直接跳上去部機都唔得咩？定係都係會響？<br />\n跳上去可能跳多幾次仲會爛埋"},{"pid":"e93a1986e6101ebc617c3f8b7932306085c33280","tid":1525780,"uid":259329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58eb75c9c6db6979c8a6b76a81b99d672cd6c73a","tid":1525780,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:04:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界同我出機場！！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界同我出機場！！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界同我出機場！！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界同我出機場！！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界同我出機場！！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界同我出機場！！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=